VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'create an extreme close-up of the faces. The characters are kissing. And now I\'m going to use only one reference, the image that we just created. Let\'s see what happens. Well, that\'s an awkward kiss. Eyes are closed. Okay, that\'s much'

[02:28] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'better. So, you can see how easy it is to create like entire stories using this technique. For realistic characters, this will work as well, but you can see it still has a little bit of that'

[02:40] [scene:talk]
